# Go Generic Service

Plain Go service (no gRPC). Use this for Layer 1 dogfooding with Mind.

## Structure

- `code/main.go` — entrypoint (minimal HTTP health on :8080 by default)
- `code/go.mod` — module definition

## Commands

- Build: `go build ./...`
- Test: `go test ./...`
- Run: run the binary from `code/`

Replace the default main with your own logic.
